          "According to a report, an officer with the BC RCMP Traffic Services in Merritt was doing speed enforcement on the highway when he clocked the Corvette doing 243 kph. For all our American readers, that’s 150 mph. In all fairness, that kind of speed would get you thrown in jail and your car impounded pretty much anywhere."
